= Our mailing lists =

We have four mailing lists started on~[http://googlegroups.com googlegroups.com] for~experimental using.
Everybody is~welcomed to~subscribe to~them, but please be~aware that they are currently passing the~testing phase.
If~you would like to~subscribe, just send a~message to~the~address 
mentioned near each option.

== For~English users ==

* Name: luwrain-users-en@googlegroups.com
* Language: English
* Description: Discussing of~LUWRAIN using in~English
* Subscribe: [mailto:luwrain-users-en+subscribe@googlegroups.com luwrain-users-en+subscribe@googlegroups.com]

