* Subscribe: [mailto:luwrain-devel-ru+subscribe@googlegroups.com luwrain-devel-ru+subscribe@googlegroups.com]

== Old Homeros mailing lists ==

Previously we used to~talk about LUWRAIN in~ALT~Linux Homeros mailing lists.
If you would like, you still may subscribe to it.
However, now it is recommended to~use one of~the~mailing lists mentioned above,
because after 2015 we are about to~prohibit LUWRAIN discussing in~this~list as~an~offtopic.

Use the~subscription page by~this~link:

* [[http://lists.altlinux.org/mailman/listinfo/homeros/ http://lists.altlinux.org/mailman/listinfo/homeros/]]


